ygData.messageBody:
bah, half elves have nicer plate, i hate my wood elf plate, its not shiny
much and i have a Cadillac hood ornament on my head with my crested helm,
feel so stupid. Ppl constantly telling me a bird hit me in the forehead or
some stupidity like that. Half elf or human is the way to go for plate
look... as far as banded is concerned, if you want a blackened crown, i got
one from the doing the ogre head quest in kaladim first shot, i had bought
one head for 7pp and a friend got me the second one, it pays to help out
lower level friends sometimes as they hunt these zones and see whats being
given away/sold in them hehe (Cornflunk and Zarchoomi). you go to the
warrior guild, the dwarf that gives the goblin beads quest, i forgot his
name but give him the 2 heads, he'll give ya blackened armor, i got a crown,
maybe its effected as to what level you are, i was in the 20's when i did
this quest. Cant wait to get a guise of the deceiver to morph into a dark
elf. Then again, the dark elf helm is nice but has a nasty overbite 8)

Minkin Nehoc
Sol Ro
